Release 1.21:
AP Password Updated: Changed the fallback Access Point password to new one.
Dynamic Live Step Updates (Real-Time Actuation): When modifying a step using the web UI, the code now checks if the edited instruction is the currently executing step. If it is, it explicitly compares the new values against the actively working hardware states (lastTemperature and lastFanSpeed). If a change is detected, it instantly triggers the corresponding servo routines (adjustTemperature, adjustFanSpeed, and resetting the time servo via setMaximumRoastingTime) to apply the modifications immediately mid-roast.
