Release 1.24:
*1 Improved accuracy of the temperature adjustment by first setting to the maximum 240C or the minimum 150C ( whichever is closer to the last temperature)  by extra Servo duration than required. Then adjust accurate time to the target temperature from 240C or 150C. This will avoid a temperature adjustment inaccuracy to be add on to and  drifted from one adjustment to the next.  
